org.altbeacon.beacon

Class Identifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.altbeacon.beacon.Identifier

  • public class Identifier
extends Object
    Encapsulates a beacon identifier of arbitrary byte length It can encapsulate an identifier that is a 16-byte UUID, or an integer Internally this is stored as a normalized string representation for ease of serialization Created by dyoung on 7/18/14.
